##### MF3: REACTION CROSS SECTIONS                                6143 1451
                                                                  6143 1451
All the data present in the following MT-sections have been       6143 1451
calculated with TALYS, possibly normalized to experimental data.  6143 1451
If the maximal cross section in an excitation function over the   6143 1451
whole energy range does not exceed 1.e-9 b, the MT-number is not  6143 1451
included. Cross sections lower than 1.e-20 b are assumed to have  6143 1451
no physical meaning and are set to zero. All MT numbers extend up 6143 1451
to the highest incident energy.                                   6143 1451
The following reaction channels/MT numbers are generally included:6143 1451
                                                                  6143 1451
- MT1      : Total cross section                                  6143 1451
                                                                  6143 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range,    6143 1451
or partly reproduced using experimental data.                     6143 1451
                                                                  6143 1451
- MT2      : Elastic scattering cross section                     6143 1451
                                                                  6143 1451
Obtained by subtracting the non-elastic cross section from the    6143 1451
total cross section.                                              6143 1451
                                                                  6143 1451
- MT3      : Non-elastic cross section                            6143 1451
                                                                  6143 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range.    6143 1451
                                                                  6143 1451
- MT4      : Total inelastic cross section                        6143 1451
                                                                  6143 1451
Sum of MT=51-91.                                                  6143 1451
                                                                  6143 1451
- MT5      : (n,anything) cross section                           6143 1451
                                                                  6143 1451
MT5 contains the reactions which can not be stored in any other   6143 1451
