- MT2      : Elastic angular distribution                         6143 1451
                                                                  6143 1451
The flag LTT=3 is used to indicate a switch at some high energy,  6143 1451
generally 50 MeV, from a Legendre representation to a tabulated   6143 1451
representation. For incident energies below this energy, the      6143 1451
